
# EDA on Crime Data

## Project Overview
This project aims to explore and analyze crime data to uncover patterns, trends, and insights. The goal is to understand various aspects of crime occurrences, such as the types of crimes, geographical distribution, and temporal trends, through data analysis and visualization.
